üîπ 1. IP Subnetting and Network Design
We‚Äôre given:

MSIS IP Range: 192.168.2.0/24

MIT IP Range: 192.168.44.0/24


‚úÖ MSIS Subnetting (192.168.2.0/24)
LAN           Hosts   Needed	  Nearest   Subnet	  CIDR	  Network	  Broadcast	  Usable IP Range	  Usable Hosts
MSIS LAN A	  102	    128	      /25	   192.168.2.0	  192.168.2.127	  192.168.2.1 ‚Äì 192.168.2.126	126
MSIS LAN D	  28	    32	      /27	  192.168.2.128	  192.168.2.159	  192.168.2.129 ‚Äì 192.168.2.158	30
MSIS LAN B	  13	    16	    /28	  192.168.2.160	  192.168.2.175	  192.168.2.161 ‚Äì 192.168.2.174	14
MSIS LAN C	  6	       8	    /29	  192.168.2.176	  192.168.2.183	  192.168.2.177 ‚Äì 192.168.2.182	6

‚úÖ MIT Subnetting (192.168.44.0/24)
LAN	Hosts Needed	Nearest Subnet	CIDR	Network	Broadcast	Usable IP Range	Usable Hosts
